        <title>International Megan's Law of 2008</title>
      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To mandate reporting requirements for convicted sex traffickers and other sex offenders intending to engage in international travel, to provide advance notice of convicted sex offenders who intend to travel outside the United States to the government of the country of destination, to prevent entry into the United States by any foreign sex offender, and for other purposes.</title>
